FR: Mon but, dans le cadre de mon doctorat, est d'optimiser les systèmes de Test & Trace en implémentant des algorithmes en bioinformatique et en machine learning. Concrètement, je développe des plugins pour Go.Data, un outil de surveillance épidémiologique développé par l'OMS.

EN: The goal of my project is to optimise the Test & Trace system with the use of bioinformatics and machine learning techniques. To do so, I develop plugins for the outbreak investigation tool Go.Data, which has been developed by the WHO.

column12: The general aim of my research is to provide a reference test-case with a first quantitative description of the relationships between agroecological farming, biodiversity of wild bees as crop pollinators and cucurbits crop production in sub-Saharan Africa. Furthermore, a socioeconomic analysis produced on cost-benefits, sustainability and productivity of small-scale cucurbits farming will also be of interest for the development of a more sustainable agriculture in Africa. Applying this on the African mainland has not been done before.
